title: 6 Chinese military observers arrive in Syria
description: DAMASCUS， May 14 (Xinhua) -- Six Chinese working as United Nations (UN) military observers arrived in the Syrian capital of Damascus to join the 189-member team already on ground to monitor the ceasefire， upon the UN's request.
